<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1916-12-12T09:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1916-12-12T09:00:00-05:00" n="1281" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1281">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 819.11D29/155</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Price</persName> to the
                                    <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                            </hi>
                        </head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                        </opener>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                                    <hi rend="italic">Panama</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1916-12-12T09:00:00-05:00">
                                    <hi rend="italic">December 12, 1916, 9 a.m.</hi>
                                </date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Panaman Minister for Foreign Affairs has sent to me remittance for twelve
                            thousand three hundred and fifty dollars stating that it is in payment
                            of award of arbitration award Fourth of July riot on account of the
                            death of one and wounding sixteen Americans. Same will be forwarded by
                            mail steamer tomorrow.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Price</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>